  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Cut flatbread into 1-inch (2.5 cm) squares.",
    "In a shallow dish, mix together almond flour, egg, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Dip each flatbread square into the almond flour mixture, coating both sides.",
    "Place coated flatbread squares on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.",
